1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 4=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,320
(Zhou's Fabrics)
Give us our money back!

18
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:20,120
- Refund!
- Refund!

19
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:22,960
Li Yunhe,

20
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:24,480
I don't think you should go in there.

21
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,960
They'll tear you to pieces.

22
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,680
I'll go.

23
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:28,920
No, let me go.

24
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,480
If we don't salvage our reputation now,

25
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,680
we'll be buried in an avalanche.

26
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,680
Hey, wait for me.

27
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,680
Sorry, excuse me.

28
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:36,880
Move aside. Coming through.

29
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,200
Who are you?
Ever heard of waiting your turn?

30
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,160
I'm Li Yunhe,

31
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:41,920
the Zhou son-in-law.

32
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,360
Are you really Li Yunhe?

33
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:44,800
The one and only.

34
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,000
Mr. Li, Yu,

35
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,960
you finally made it.

36
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,880
Are you alright?

37
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:48,880
Sir,

38
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,920
is he Li Yunhe, the one who claimed

39
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,680
Zhou's Fabrics had tribute-grade

40
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,440
Rustling Silk?

41
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,320
That would be me.

42
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,520
Do you even know

43
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:56,960
who this gentleman is?

44
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,400
How dare you scam him?

45
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,920
If we don't get our money back today,

46
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,600
I swear

47
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,280
I'll torch this shop to the ground.

48
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,880
You've got some nerve here.

49
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,120
Li Yunhe.

50
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,120
I'm not an unreasonable man.

51
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:10,320
You're the one who went on and on
about how great this silk was.

52
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:12,320
I spent a fortune placing an order.

53
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,200
Don't worry, sir.

54
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,080
You'll get

55
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,920
your money back.

56
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,080
What about ours?

57
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,000
And ours?

58
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,960
And ours?

59
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,120
What about our money?

60
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,760
Everyone,

61
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,800
rest assured,

62
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,800
you'll all get your money back.

63
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,880
If you don't trust me,

64
00:02:24,880 --> 00:02:27,000
surely you trust
the Zhous' century-old reputation.

65
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,760
My lord! My lord!

66
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,160
Oh,

67
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,360
my lord.

68
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,920
Li Yunhe

69
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:35,960
has shown his face!

70
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:39,520
Are the men I told you to plant
in place?

71
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:42,000
All in position, ready to go.

72
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:43,520
When the moment is right,

73
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,400
our people will lead the charge
to loot and smash

74
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,920
Zhou's Fabrics.

75
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:52,560
My lord,
just sit back and enjoy the show.

76
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,280
Your Majesty,

77
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,280
Li Yunhe

78
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,480
has finally appeared.

79
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,480
Oh, really?

80
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,520
Let's go take a look.

81
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,920
After you,

82
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,560
my lord.

83
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,160
My lord.

84
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:29,160
Hey, you there.

85
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,680
Are you trying to block the way

86
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,360
on behalf of your master?

87
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,200
Zhang Tao, don't.

88
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,680
- After you, my lord.
- After you, my lord.

89
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,560
Stay out of my lord's way.

90
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,000
The Marquis's heir
certainly has an attitude.

91
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,600
Who are those people?

92
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:07,680
My lord, that man is the new owner
of Xianquan Tavern.

93
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,680
Word has it that he's from the capital.

94
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,600
Send someone to dig into his background.

95
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,480
Find out who he is.

96
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:16,000
Understood.

97
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:31,820
(Zhou's Fabrics)

98
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,360
Folks of Feng City,

99
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,560
thank you for taking the time

100
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,400
out of your busy day to be here.

101
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,360
As the Zhou son-in-law,

102
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,080
on behalf of the Zhou family,

103
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:48,160
on behalf of our Rustling Silk,

104
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,680
first, I must say to you all,

105
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,560
I'm sorry.

106
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,400
What good is saying sorry?

107
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,360
Give us our money back!

108
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,480
You hyped up defective junk
as tribute-grade?

109
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,320
You never took us seriously!

110
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,960
Total scammers.

111
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,680
Refund!

112
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:05,800
- Refund!
- We want our money back!

113
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,360
- Refund!
- I demand a refund!

114
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,000
- Refund now!
- Refund!

115
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,640
If you don't refund us,

116
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:12,000
we'll smash this shop!

117
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,320
Let's tear this place down!

118
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:18,120
Let's smash it all!

119
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,760
Yes! Smash it to pieces!

120
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,560
Those merchants
are so heartless and shady.

121
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,920
Just burn the whole place down!

122
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,520
Making such a racket in public,

123
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,360
have you no shame?

124
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,840
Hey, I placed ten orders!

125
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,200
He scammed me out of 200 taels
with his fakes.

126
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,200
What's wrong
with a little schadenfreude?

127
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,320
I wouldn't celebrate just yet.

128
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,520
Judging by the look on his face,

129
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,640
he's not just sitting there
awaiting his doom.

130
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,520
The Zhous' Rustling Silk
has been of poor quality

131
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,960
for ages. It's not new.

132
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:42,720
There's no way

133
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,400
Li Yunhe can pull off a miracle.

134
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,360
It's not as simple as you think.

135
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,200
Just watch the show.

136
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,520
Everyone, calm down.

137
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,320
Please, calm down.

138
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,640
The Zhou family members
are all right here.

139
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,840
Getting worked up like this

140
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,320
won't solve anything.

141
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,720
Yunhe,

142
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,240
do you have a way to resolve

143
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,360
this situation?

144
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,560
Can't you see?

145
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,320
That's exactly what I'm trying to do.

146
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:06,720
How about this?

147
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,160
I'll cover the losses.

148
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,320
You'll cover them?

149
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,360
In return, I want the Zhous' partnership

150
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,520
for the overseas Rustling Silk business.

151
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,000
What kind of partnership?

152
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,400
You get thirty percent, I get seventy.

153
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,720
That's my final offer.

154
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,400
Can't you see

155
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,200
that someone is setting you up today?

156
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,920
Mr. Xie, right?

157
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,360
I think you might want to see

158
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,840
what happens next

159
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:33,800
before making your move.

160
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,120
We want our money back!

161
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,520
- Get me a refund!
- Refund!

162
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,580
- Refund!
- Refund!

163
00:06:39,580 --> 00:06:40,500
Silence!

164
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:43,640
Don't let a single one get away.

165
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,600
Borrowed authority?

166
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:48,720
I didn't expect

167
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,200
Li Yunhe to actually

168
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,280
call in the authorities to quell this.

169
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,040
He has the nerve
to summon the constables?

170
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,040
Are you bandits or what?

171
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,440
You dare to riot

172
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,440
in the streets

173
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,640
under His Majesty's rule?

174
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,440
Have you no regard for the law?

175
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,120
Feng City's constables?

176
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,360
(Zhou's Fabrics)
Whose shop is this?

177
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,160
I'm Li Yunhe, the live-in son-in-law
of the Zhous.

178
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,360
Greetings, Constable Xing.

179
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:20,840
Li Yunhe? This shop belongs
to the Zhous?

180
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,000
Indeed, it does.

181
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:25,040
I received a report
from concerned citizens

182
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:27,120
that there is a public disturbance here.

183
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,920
Are they the ones causing trouble?

184
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,520
We've been wronged, sir.

185
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,040
We're not bandits.

186
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,520
We're here to get a refund.

187
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:35,040
The Zhous passed off shoddy goods
as top quality.

188
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,440
We just want justice.

189
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,040
Constable Xing,

190
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,840
please, you must stand up for us.

191
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,920
- Stand up for us!
- Stand up for us!

192
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,480
- Stand up for us!
- We want justice!

193
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,440
Silence!

194
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,520
Li Yunhe, they say

195
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,840
the Zhous' shop is
selling shoddy goods as top-quality.

196
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,040
Is that true?

197
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:50,920
Constable Xing,

198
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:54,440
it's a long story.

199
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,720
Oh, right.

200
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,560
I have a question, Constable Xing.

201
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,440
They say they received word

202
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:00,760
that the Zhous' Rustling Silk

203
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,160
is about to
lose its imperial tribute status.

204
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,680
Is that the case?

205
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,960
That is indeed true.

206
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,440
Soon enough,

207
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:13,280
the Weaving Bureau will dispatch
a formal notice to the Zhou family.

208
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,480
In other words,

209
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,040
that notice from the Weaving Bureau

210
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,920
has not yet been delivered to us,

211
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,160
which means

212
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,840
when you bought the Rustling Silk,

213
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,480
it hadn't

214
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,760
yet been stripped of its tribute status.

215
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,440
So, the Rustling Silk you hold

216
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,760
is now a limited edition

217
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,040
of imperial tribute Rustling Silk.

218
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,840
Right?

219
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,040
Don't twist the facts!

220
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,240
If not for the imperial tribute label,

221
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,640
who'd buy your junk?

222
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,240
Exactly!

223
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,320
If not for the imperial tribute label,

224
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,480
who would want this stuff?

225
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,880
Give us our money back!

226
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,440
- We want our money back!
- Refund!

227
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,920
- Refund!
- Refund!

228
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,560
- Refund!
- Refund!

229
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,640
Quiet down!

230
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:49,920
Our Rustling Silk
has a hundred-year heritage.

231
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,120
The reason it became an imperial tribute

232
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,840
is simple.

233
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,840
It was built on uncompromising quality

234
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,120
and a golden reputation.

235
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,080
Now,

236
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,840
though the tribute status is revoked,

237
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,120
and you may be disgruntled,

238
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,040
I accept that.

239
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,880
I'll honor every single refund.

240
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,840
But I believe

241
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,720
once our new Gambiered Silk,

242
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,360
our new tribute-grade Gambiered Silk,

243
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:11,320
is unveiled and meets you all again,

244
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,000
you will

245
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,800
still choose us.

246
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,760
My lord,
the Zhous are clearly in the wrong,

247
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,480
and Li Yunhe actually dared
to call the constables.

248
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,200
Now that the authorities are here,

249
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,680
we should pull our men out.

250
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:29,380
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)

251
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,680
Yu, do you like the name?

252
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,080
I love it.

253
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,080
Everyone,

254
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,480
today, with you as our witnesses,

255
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,920
Zhou's Fabrics

256
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:41,360
is officially renamed
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk.

257
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,520
- Wonderful!
- Terrific!

258
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,480
Yu,

259
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,680
you and Chunxiang will handle

260
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,560
the refunds

261
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,000
for our pre-order customers.

262
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:50,600
Alright.

263
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:51,520
Esteemed customers,

264
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,320
please follow me inside.

265
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:54,280
Please line up.

266
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,760
Yunzhuo.

267
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:12,560
I think Li Yunhe

268
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,560
is at his wits' end.

269
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,640
So what if the constables showed up?

270
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:18,000
He still has to issue refunds.

271
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:21,160
Mr. Wang, what's your take?

272
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,840
I believe
Her Highness is absolutely right.

273
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,640
You two are such blockheads.

274
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,200
Didn't you see Lu Qifeng

275
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,840
storm off just now?

276
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,560
So what?

277
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:33,600
Lu Qifeng is just frustrated

278
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,680
that he couldn't crush Li Yunhe

279
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,040
in one fell swoop.

280
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:38,880
Li Yunhe used the authorities

281
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,960
to draw a clear dividing line in time

282
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,560
for the Rustling Silk
that the Zhous sold.

283
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,760
He's declared that from now on,

284
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:48,000
the Zhous will only sell
tribute-grade Rustling Silk.

285
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,200
Until the Zhous deliver on that,

286
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,240
Lu Qifeng

287
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:53,160
will struggle to find an excuse
to cause more trouble.

288
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,560
I get it now.

289
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:57,600
Li Yunhe is creating an illusion.

290
00:10:57,760 --> 00:11:00,440
What Zhou's Fabrics sold
were cheap goods,

291
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,960
and what Tang Xian Gambiered Silk sells

292
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,840
are all tribute-grade,

293
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,160
high-end, premium products.

294
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:06,160
But

295
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,400
the Zhous' tribute-grade Rustling Silk

296
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,840
wasn't even that good to begin with.

297
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,080
So, from here on, their survival

298
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,040
hinges on whether Li Yunhe

299
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,040
can actually deliver

300
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,880
tribute-grade Rustling Silk.

301
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:20,320
Does Li Yunhe
even have that kind of ability?

302
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,680
Hard to say.

303
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,400
Keep a close eye on the Zhou Manor.

304
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:26,240
Especially Li Yunhe.

305
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,600
I have a hunch

306
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,440
that his name will soon
resound throughout Feng City.

307
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,120
Yes, Your Majesty.

308
00:11:35,980 --> 00:11:38,980
(Zhou's Dyehouse)

309
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,280
Yu!

310
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:46,640
Have you lost your mind?

311
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,800
What now?

312
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,120
Do you have any idea what you've done?

313
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,040
What have I done?

314
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,400
Why rename the perfectly good

315
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,440
Zhou's Fabrics?

316
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,200
And

317
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,720
why did you change Rustling Silk

318
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,080
to Gambiered Silk?

319
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,840
Was it Li Yunhe

320
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,240
who gave you this "brilliant" idea?

321
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,080
You know full well

322
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,880
the situation our family is in.

323
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,920
If we don't follow Li Yunhe's plan,

324
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:05,880
the Zhou family's troubles

325
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,240
will only multiply.

326
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,320
In Feng City,

327
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:10,560
this silk has been called Rustling Silk
for centuries.

328
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,120
If you suddenly change the name,

329
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,000
from now on,

330
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,920
who will even know

331
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:14,840
our shop

332
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,440
sells Rustling Silk?

333
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,600
Gambiered Silk is Rustling Silk.

334
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,320
We changed the name

335
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,720
to set ourselves apart

336
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,760
from all the other Rustling Silks

337
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:22,920
on the market,

338
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:24,560
to let everyone know
that the Zhou family's

339
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,640
is tribute-grade

340
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:27,120
and far better quality than the rest.

341
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,720
"Tribute-grade"? You dare

342
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,520
use those words?

343
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,120
We've already been stripped

344
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:32,160
of the imperial tribute status.

345
00:12:32,400 --> 00:12:33,200
If our quality is great,

346
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,640
why can't we say so?

347
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,400
Great quality?

348
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,800
If it's so great,
why was the status revoked?

349
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:39,520
That was then.

350
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,920
Now it's different.

351
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:41,720
Bring it here.

352
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,120
See for yourself.

353
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,800
Here's our finished silk now.

354
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,920
Not bad.

355
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:52,000
It really is different.

356
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:54,600
Compared to what we had before,

357
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,320
whether in smoothness

358
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,720
or luster,

359
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,360
this is vastly superior.

360
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,160
That's why

361
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,920
Li Yunhe now dares to say

362
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,240
our Gambiered Silk

363
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,360
is tribute-grade.

364
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,440
Yu, how did you pull this off?

365
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,440
It wasn't me.
I don't have that kind of skill.

366
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,520
It was Li Yunhe.

367
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:11,920
He scoured ancient texts,

368
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,160
dragged me and Chunxiang

369
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,400
all over the place,

370
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,320
and ran countless experiments.

371
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:16,920
We barely managed

372
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:17,520
to restore

373
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,280
and improve

374
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:19,920
the core craft of Gambiered Silk.

375
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,920
He actually pulled that off?

376
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,360
Yeah.

377
00:13:27,780 --> 00:13:30,580
(Zhou Manor)

378
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:32,040
Once I've earned enough money,

379
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,160
I'll take Yu away from here

380
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:35,320
to make a fresh start.

381
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:37,400
You two aren't going anywhere.

382
00:14:09,620 --> 00:14:13,220
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

383
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:16,580
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

384
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:19,820
♪Who took the March rain♪

385
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:23,420
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

386
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:26,580
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

387
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:29,940
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

388
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:36,740
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

389
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:40,220
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

390
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:43,300
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

391
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:45,740
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

392
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:49,940
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

393
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:53,300
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

394
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:56,580
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

395
00:14:57,100 --> 00:15:00,020
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

396
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:06,700
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

397
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:36,500
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

398
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:39,900
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

399
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:43,220
♪Who took the March rain♪

400
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:46,740
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

401
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:50,020
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

402
00:15:50,100 --> 00:15:53,820
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

403
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:57,140
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

404
00:15:57,140 --> 00:16:00,100
♪As seasons change♪

405
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:03,740
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

406
00:16:03,740 --> 00:16:06,580
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

407
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:09,220
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

408
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:13,300
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

409
00:16:13,300 --> 00:16:16,620
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

410
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:20,340
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

411
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:23,860
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

412
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:26,740
♪Only for you♪

413
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:30,340
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

414
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:33,220
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

415
00:16:33,340 --> 00:16:35,900
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

416
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:39,980
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

417
00:16:39,980 --> 00:16:43,300
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

418
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:46,700
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

419
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:53,220
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

420
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:58,420
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

421
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:04,220
♪Your wedding gown♪
